{"tid":1501530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"825入機場","createTime":"2019-08-24T11:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T11:34:16.000Z","uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"019cbded6de3c7796554ab7e3d7a42ab790958a1","tid":1501530,"uid":259613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:29:45.000Z","msg":"[黑警還眼] 又爆眼？825全民入機場<br />\n<br />\n見Post者開新Post洗連登，重現812<br />\n<br />\n唔理825有咩活動，聽日11am起一律入機場，勢要塞爆機場！<br />\n<br />\n如果你仲有良心，有些少良知，唔理你和理非定勇武，825你一定要出現，為我哋嘅手足討回公道。香港人已經唔可以再俾警察恰到上心口。眼又爆，腳又斷，下一步就係手足斷送生命！<br />\n<br />\n係警察迫香港人，呢班警察為人工福利，不講仁義道德，迫香港上絕路。<br />\n<br />\n825唔塞爆機場，誓不為香港人。<br />\n<br />\n今次核爆都唔離開機場<br />\n因為香港人已經冇路走<br />\n行入機場，你有本事就打橫抬我哋出嚟<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油，機場見<br />\n<br />\n限時機場公海Link：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NWbhCkrIxUTLo9sjsE9Xaw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNWbhCkrIxUTLo9sjsE9Xaw&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=ffadb413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NWbhCkrIxUTLo9sjsE9Xaw</a><br />\n<br />\nChannel: <a href=\"https://t.me/walkin_airport_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwalkin_airport_news&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOpbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=21a77af8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/walkin_airport_news</a>"},{"pid":"0da97d9b0ce13d20844928c9fbc6fe61993a0680","tid":1501530,"uid":78300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打狗！ 救人！</span></span><br />\n荃葵照去"},{"pid":"d6d5db6c362ce6841dd917ab274302d58024793d","tid":1501530,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:34:16.000Z","msg":"825荃葵青大遊行<br />\n1430葵涌運動場"}]}